title: Cake Island
description: High stakes and tasty bakes. Four eligible singles think they have the recipe for love. But on this island, some of the suitors are made… of cake.
altHero: building that looks like a round cake
alt1: man with cake on his mouth, bewildered that his bride is made of cake
alt2: man comforts woman as she points angrily
alt3: man with cake for a head
alt4: man and woman kiss a slice of cake
